                <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>eliae</ex></expan> Candidae <expan><abbr>q</abbr><ex>uondam</ex></expan> quae vixit annos <lb n="2"/>XXV <expan><abbr>Sep</abbr><ex>timius</ex></expan> Priscus eques <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>ad</abbr><ex>iutricis</ex></expan> con<lb break="no" n="3"/>iugi carissim<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sarkophagkasten. Z. 1: Buchstabe Q für q(uondam) mit waagrechter Querhaste in der Mitte.</p>
